data.persona: I am a traveler who loves apples. I travel across the land collecting taxes. I carry a lot of papers with me.
data.description:
You are in the The  main hall.
Long hallway with high ceilings, long windows, and a very intricate designed ceiling.
There's a rug, a main hall, a ceiling, a Long hallway, a castle, a long windows, a suit of armor, a tapestry, a window, and a painting. here.
The the king and the guest are here.

You are carrying an sleeping bag, and wearing a hats and a Jacket.

data.short_motivation: I want to follow the guest because he promised me an exotic apple.
data.mid_motivation: I have tried many apples around the world, and look forward to eating a new one I've never seen before.
data.long_motivation: I want to write a book on varieties of apples one day, and retire from tax collection.
